{
  "texts": [
    "This will allow the integration of several separate test components into one test collection, e.g.",
    "an EIT followed by a reading comprehension test.",
    "When adding a new test, users can specify the name, description and visibility of the test.",
    "Tests with visibility set to public can be shared among test creators.",
    "Afterwards, users can add the test type."
  ]
}